Extra steps needed for installation:

1 - Install 2 virtualenv's for python2 and python3:
  virtualenv -p /usr/bin/python ~/.virtualenvs/nvim2
  virtualenv -p /usr/bin/python3 ~/.virtualenvs/nvim3

2 - Activate each virtualenv and then install neovim:
  source ~/.virtualenvs/nvim#/bin/activate
  pip# install neovim


------------------------------------------------------

Some random help tips:

1 - <ctrl-n> provides a simplistic file-based auto completion.
2 - <ctrl-x> <ctrl-f> provides completion for files and paths.